<emphasis id="61B6EAB4FFF0FFEEE1FD03D1FE2AFC66" bold="true" box="[199,393,906,933]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="33">M. phoebe abbas</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="37534B57FFF0FFEEE0B503D0FDD7FC66" author="Gross, F. J. &amp; Ebert, G." box="[399,628,906,933]" pageId="8" pageNumber="33" pagination="8 - 45" refId="ref9178" refString="Gross, F. J. &amp; Ebert, G. (1975) Beitrage zur Kenntis der Rhopaloceren Irans. 2. Beitrag. Neue Taxa der Pieridae, Satyridae und Nymphalidae. Journal of the Entomological Society of Iran Supplement, 1, 8 - 45." type="journal article" year="1975">Gross &amp; Ebert, 1975</bibRefCitation>
